Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Il mio primo eterno amore{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Se ti dimenticavo sarei vissuta felicemente, ma sembra che la mia memoria abbia deciso di tornare in questo parchetto da sola.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}La tua mancanza è stata una ferita dolorosa per tutto questo tempo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Desidero unicamente liberarmi da questo dolore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sembrano squisiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne vuoi uno?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delizioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sento un buon profumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi sono messa un profumo di mia mamma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veramente buono.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nota iniziale al bergamotto e persistenza al cioccolato.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cosa vuol dire?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.18,0:01:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veramente non l'ho capito nemmeno io.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sei pronta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Non ancora!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sei pronta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sono pronta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scusami. Ti ho svegliata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buon giorno, Lady Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buon giorno, Kirin.
